------------------------------------------------------------
DIFFICULTY
------------------------------------------------------------
Difficulty Level     : Very Hard / Challenging
Elden Ring is widely regarded as a very difficult game,
consistent with FromSoftware's Soulslike pedigree. However,
compared to previous titles, it is considered slightly more
approachable due to:
  - Open-world freedom to grind and over-level
  - Spirit Ash summons (AI companions in boss fights)
  - Greater build variety and flexibility
  - Ability to skip difficult areas and return later

Despite these accommodations, many bosses are considered
among the hardest in gaming history (e.g., Malenia, Blade
of Miquella).

